These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, family
City: marseilles, nizza
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
There 2 different types of food: apple, pumpkin
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
4. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | family     |
| City   | nizza     | marseilles |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Food         | pumpkin   | apple       |

