.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
City: miami, prague
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, horror
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, nigerian
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| City          | prague     | miami     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | horror        |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | blues         |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian       |
| Transport         | roller  | quad-bike |

