The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, satire
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, november
There 2 different types of food: cherry, apricot
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the fisherman##1
4. the musician is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage      | tea        | fanta     |
| Job           | musician   | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | horror    |
| Birthday           | september    | november    |
| Food         | cherry | apricot   |

